        "Description": "Do you know what makes\r\nMizutsune fins so special? Why,\r\nit\u0027s their outstanding resistance\r\nto water and exquisite pattern!\r\nMaking clothes from those will\r\nsurely net us more foot traffic.\r\nThink of the Outpost\u0027s future!",
